  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>The Hotel Tetras Lodge is on either half board or bed &amp; breakfast. Please note that on selected dates half board is obligatory.</p>
<p> </p>
<p>A continental breakfast is served each morning often including locally sourced yogurts, cheese, meats, bread and pastries.</p>
<p>Enjoy a three course evening meal in the Le Tetras restaurant, the menu is inspired by regional cuisine and often includes seafood and meat dishes.</p>
<p> </p>
<p>New Years Eve gala dinner included.</p>
<p> </p>
<p><strong>Obligatory half board dates</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>23rd December </li>
<li>30th December </li>
<li>10th February</li>
<li>17th February</li>
</ul>]]></cateringDescription>
