  <description><![CDATA[<p>Hotel Tetras Lodge is located in the resort centre of <a data-udi="umb://document/204ce8e4cf8c4ab09205501e16cb7565" href="/{localLink:umb://document/204ce8e4cf8c4ab09205501e16cb7565}" title="Tignes">Tignes Les Brevieres</a>, with lovely mountain and village views and close to the slopes. You can also enjoy the bar and lounge or wellness area after a day on the slopes.</p>
<h2>Cosy hotel</h2>
<p>The Hotel Tetras Lodge is an authentic Savoyard hotel in Tignes, with warm and cosy atmosphere. <span>All of the rooms are designed in a modern yet cosy style, with many of the rooms offering spectacular views across the resort and surrounding mountains.</span></p>
<h2><span>Refined cuisine</span></h2>
<p><span>Le Tetras, the hotel’s own restaurant serves delicious dishes for lunch and dinner, serving a twist on regional specialities.  For guests staying on half board, you can enjoy a three course evening meal each day with a varied menu, often including seafood starters, hearty main courses and French desserts. Le Tetras </span>is a great choice if you are meeting friends and family down in the resort for a bite to eat, best enjoyed on the sunny terrace. </p>
<h2>Relaxation</h2>
<p><span>After a day of exploring the wonderful ski area, sit back and relax in front of the fireplace, and enjoy a speciality crafted cocktail from the hotel bar or ta</span>ke the time to sit back and relax in the hotels lovely wellness area which features a hot tub, sauna and steam room which is located on the terrace. </p>
<p> </p>]]></description>
